## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data and reports up to October 2023. The situation is dynamic, and ongoing developments in the labor market and public health policies may influence the shortage. Additionally, regional variations in the shortage and responses by different school districts may not be fully captured in this report. Further research could explore long-term solutions and the effectiveness of current interventions.